OL,3,CMan jailed for blinding father-of-two
OL,4,Cin 'sickening' glass attack
OL,6,FMr Syron, who had moved from Leeds to
OL,7,FAustralia with his fiancee and
OL,8,Fchildren, was visiting friends and
OL,9,Ffamily in his home city for Christmas
OL,10,Fwhen he was attacked by 37-year-old
OL,11,FGareth Dean.
OL,13,FLeeds Crown Court heard that "in an
OL,14,Finstant, his life was ruined in so
OL,15,Fmany ways."
OL,17,FMr Syron has not been able to return
OL,18,Fto Australia since, and has missed key
OL,19,Fmilestones in his children's lives,
OL,20,Fincluding his little girl's first
OL,21,Fsteps, the court was told.
