OL,6,F"He describes panicking, everything
OL,7,Fgoing black."
OL,9,FA witness described the blow as being
OL,10,Fadministered "with force."
OL,12,FThe court heard Mr Syron's brother
OL,13,Frecalled him screaming that he could
OL,14,Fnot see.
OL,16,FDean went to another bar, before
OL,17,Fhanding himself in days later. The
OL,18,Fcourt heard Dean had been drinking
OL,19,Fsince 11am and had downed at least 15
OL,20,Fpints of lager.
