OL,4,Cin 'sickening' glass attack
OL,6,FThe court heard that since the attack,
OL,7,Fhis life - and his family's - has been
OL,8,Fturned upside down, and their
OL,9,Ffinancial future is "precarious," with
OL,10,Fall hopes invested in returning to
OL,11,FAustralia soon.
OL,13,FJudge Richard Mansell KC said this
OL,14,Fwill not happen for at least six to
OL,15,Feight weeks, and he will have to
OL,16,Freturn to the UK for treatment.
