OL,3,CMan jailed for blinding father-of-two
OL,4,Cin 'sickening' glass attack
OL,6,FIn a statement Mr Syron said: "This
OL,7,Fhas taken everything from me - my
OL,8,Fbusiness is suffering, my family is
OL,9,Fsuffering, I'm not there to bring
OL,10,Fmoney in. This is affecting my whole
OL,11,Fentire family.
OL,13,F"I am depending on people I've not
OL,14,Fdepended on since I was a child. I
OL,15,Fcan't put toothpaste onto my
OL,16,Ftoothbrush without someone helping me.
OL,17,FI have to get someone to put my
OL,18,Fclothes in place so I can get dressed.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/13
