OL,3,CMan jailed for blinding father-of-two
OL,4,Cin 'sickening' glass attack
OL,6,F"I've gone from someone not needing
OL,7,Fanyone to being a 32-year-old like a
OL,8,Fbaby. I can't explain how soul-
OL,9,Fdestroying it is."
OL,11,FHis fiancee, Kione, said in a
OL,12,Fstatement: "Instead of planning a
OL,13,Fhomecoming, I am planning appointments
OL,14,Fwith a carer. We'd been planning our
OL,15,Fwedding and to keep the business
OL,16,Fgoing. Our dream to have more children
OL,17,Fhas been put on hold.
OL,19,FDean admitted causing grievous bodily
OL,20,Fharm with intent.
