OL,4,Cin 'sickening' glass attack
OL,6,FHe was sentenced to 10 years and eight
OL,7,Fmonths in prison, with an extended
OL,8,Flicence period of five years.
OL,10,FDet Insp Dan Ridgway, of Leeds
OL,11,FDistrict CID, said: "This was a
OL,12,Fhorrendous, unprovoked attack on a man
OL,13,Fout enjoying the Boxing Day
OL,14,Fcelebrations.
