OL,6,F"I know the injuries that the victim
OL,7,Fsuffered during this assault continue
OL,8,Fto have a massive impact on not only
OL,9,Fhis life, but that of his family too.
OL,10,FI can only hope the fact Dean is now
OL,11,Fbehind bars offers the victim and his
OL,12,Ffamily some comfort as they continue
OL,13,Fto deal with the devastating
OL,14,Fconsequences of this attack.
