OL,6,F"We will not tolerate such wanton
OL,7,Fviolence in our night-time economy.
OL,8,FThe swift and effective investigation
OL,9,Fin this case meant that Dean was
OL,10,Fidentified and arrested within days of
OL,11,Fthis assault and has now faced justice
OL,12,Ffor his actions."
OL,14,FWell-wishers raised more than #58,000
OL,15,Ffor Mr Syron in the wake of the
OL,16,Fattack, which left him needing 40
OL,17,Fstitches in his eyes.
